"""agenttop — TUI for launchd jobs + Claude Code usage (htop-style).

Two-pane vertical split:
  Left  — launchd jobs from ~/Library/LaunchAgents, /Library/LaunchAgents,
          /Library/LaunchDaemons.
  Right — Claude Code usage from ~/.claude/projects/**/*.jsonl
          5h rolling window, per-model + per-project breakdown, active
          sessions, 7-day history. Per-session live tail.

Auto-refreshes every 2s. Zero deps — Python stdlib (curses + json).

Global keys:
  q / Q     quit
  Tab       cycle pane focus
  r         force refresh

Left pane (launchd) — keys active when focused:
  / (slash) filter (Enter to apply, Esc to cancel)    c clear filter
  j / ↓     down                                       k / ↑   up
  g / G     top / bottom
  Enter     follow log live (any key returns)
  R         restart selected job (kickstart -k)
  s         stop selected job (SIGTERM)

Right pane (Claude) — keys active when focused:
  j / ↓     down                                       k / ↑   up
  Enter     tail selected session (live token stream)
  v         cycle window: 5h → today → 7d → 5h
"""

